Subject: [PATCH 3/9] feat(image-gen): add Civitai image generation provider

Add a Civitai Orchestration API image generation backend for SDXL/Illustrious AIR checkpoints and LoRAs.

The provider keeps Civitai-specific networking self-contained: it shells out to curl with proxy environment variables stripped to avoid Cloudflare/Python TLS issues, without adding a generic local-execution hook or writing secrets into temporary scripts.

Includes direct provider coverage for payload construction, model selection, LoRA parsing, failure handling, curl dispatch, and text-only modality reporting.

Co-authored-by: Nako <280596805+nakoagent@users.noreply.github.com>

